{"tid":1017450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西環男子墮樓亡　神枱前滿佈血迹","createTime":"2019-02-11T12:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T13:01:10.000Z","uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6519ccd8b87294b1c032e1cdb2976ecc09b15a65","tid":1017450,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190211/large/1549843726_8e57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190211%2Flarge%2F1549843726_8e57.jpg&h=e8eb2d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【15:35】事主有情緒病，警方經調查後相信他自殘後再墮樓輕生，事件無可疑<br />\n【14:00】鑑證科人員及政府化驗師到場<br />\n<br />\n西環皇后大道西513至519號尼斯花園，清晨6時許，一名48歲、身形瘦削的男子，被發現頭部重創流血，昏迷倒卧大廈平台。救護員趕到將他送院，可惜不治。<br />\n有清潔工表示，凌晨1時許曾聽到巨響，當時未有為意，至清晨才發現有人倒卧平台。<br />\n警方初步懷疑事主由毗鄰的景賜大廈墮下，跌落尼斯花園平台，早上有警員取來保護袍到景賜大廈樓上單位調查。<br />\n<br />\n約10時許，死者母親及胞兄到場協助了解事件。據悉，事主所住單位內血迹斑斑，神枱前更滿佈血迹，懷疑他曾在神枱前不斷叩頭至流血，稍後死者母及胞兄由警員陪同前往醫院認屍。消息表示，事主本身患有情緒病多年，獨居上址，疑病發在屋內撼頭落地，致頭破血流，再攀窗墮樓，由於屋內滿佈血迹，一度引起警方懷疑另有別情，經調查後證實無可疑。　<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190211/59245358\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59245358&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=e8baf893\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190211%2F59245358&h=1e5959ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190211/59245358</a>"},{"pid":"0c57de2910c0279e60196f2fc18ecc5c3c84ae23","tid":1017450,"uid":152262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"叩頭至流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca44346fe3c1b9092ce3362d5f55aefb80b6c51","tid":1017450,"uid":66078,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:45:48.000Z","msg":"諗起烏鴉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62VyGbw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62VyGbw.png&h=e25d5548&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5faaaf15d22edeb9d145ee02770f467fb156c579","tid":1017450,"uid":40052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:54:16.000Z","msg":"有個阿哥#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8114d17d9f0bae0d42f0c5e4346226107ac9e33d","tid":1017450,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:01:10.000Z","msg":"回魂夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Q-T-0nIUzsc/hqdefault.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FQ-T-0nIUzsc%2Fhqdefault.jpg&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=550b8aef\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Q-T-0nIUzsc/hqdefault.jpg</a>"}]}